What is the FRHI Hotels & Resorts Affiliate program?
• Become a partner with a premier hotel and resort brand
• Earn 5% commission on completed hotel stays made from a direct link on your site
• It’s completely free to join and easy to start reaping the rewards
• Promote all three of our luxurious international brands; Swissôtel, Fairmont and Raffles for an increased opportunity to earn commission!
If your website does not meet our quality standards or contains content that may be considered offensive, your site will not be accepted in our network.
Commission will be paid on a monthly basis. Commission Junction will reconcile all reservations that are placed and pay out a cheque on our behalf.
Where can I view my sales and earnings?
If you log in to Commission Junction’s Affiliate Network you can view all reports and earnings in one central location.

Search Policy: We do not allow Search Engine Marketing and Trademark Bidding in our program. Affiliates are not allowed to bid on terms that drive traffic to the FRHI Hotels & Resorts websites. This includes any misspellings and variations of our trademarks.
Eligibility: You are not eligible to participate in our Program if you are resident or domiciled in Connecticut, Hawaii, New Mexico or West Virginia.
